Acknowledgements
------------------------------------------------------------------------

Host-side Qualcomm DIAG capture and decoding was pioneered by projects
including QCSuper and SCAT. diaggulp does not incorporate their code — it
is a first-party implementation of just the capture step — but it stands
on the reverse-engineering and documentation those projects contributed
to the community, and interoperates with them by design.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
Dependencies
------------------------------------------------------------------------

No third-party code is incorporated into diaggulp itself. The optional
`serial` and `decode` extras install additional packages at install time;
those are distributed separately under their own licenses and are not
included in this repository.
